OL,3,CFather and son avoid jail for dumping
OL,4,C2,000 tonnes of illegal waste
OL,6,FThree men who ran an unauthorised
OL,7,Fwaste site on their farm have been
OL,8,Fsentenced after they illegally dumped
OL,9,Fmore than 40 tonnes worth of rubbish
OL,10,Foutside a council.
OL,12,FPaul Bell, 58, of Rochdale Road, Bacup
OL,13,Fpleaded guilty to failing to apply for
OL,14,Fa permit, as required by law, and
OL,15,Ffailing to comply with an enforcement
OL,16,Fnotice.
OL,18,FPaul Harrison, of Rochdale Road,
OL,19,FBacup, and father of Benjamin
OL,20,FHarrison, pleaded guilty to the same
OL,21,Fcharges.
