OL,6,FThe 51-year-old was also found guilty
OL,7,Fof the fly-tipping of 40 tonnes of
OL,8,Fwaste outside the Rossendale Borough
OL,9,FCouncil offices at Futures Park,
OL,10,FBacup.JPaul Bell, from Stockport, the
OL,11,Fdriver of the wagon responsible for
OL,12,Fthe 40 tonne fly-tip also pleaded
OL,13,Fguilty to the fly-tipping charge.
OL,14,FBenjamin Harrison received an eight-
OL,15,Fmonth custodial sentence suspended for
OL,16,F18 months.
