OL,6,FThe lorry, which was owned by Paul
OL,7,FHarrison, had already been flagged by
OL,8,FEnvironment Agency, with officers,
OL,9,Fand, which began in 2021 - a year
OL,10,Fbefore the incident.
OL,12,FThe investigation also established
OL,13,Fthousands of tonnes of waste was
OL,14,Fbrought onto the site at The Farm,
OL,15,FRochdale Road at Bacup and tipped
OL,16,Fillegally, including significant
OL,17,Fquantities of household waste and
OL,18,Fcontaminated excavation waste.
