OL,7,Fof 18 months suspended for 18 months
OL,8,Ffor all offences. He was also ordered
OL,9,Fto undertake 150 hours of unpaid work.
OL,10,FBell received an 18-month sentence
OL,11,Fsuspended for 18 months. He was also
OL,12,Fordered to undertake 150 hours unpaid
OL,13,Fwork. The court also ordered a
OL,14,Frehabilitation activity requirement of
