OL,4,C2,000 tonnes of illegal waste
OL,6,F"The sentences support the strong
OL,7,Fstance that the Council takes on
OL,8,Foffenders who blight our communities
OL,9,Fand environment and we are pleased
OL,10,Fwith the judges' decision.J"The trio
OL,11,Fhave shown little regard for the
OL,12,Fcommunity they live and operate in,
OL,13,Fand we are delighted that Operation
OL,14,FTrident has brought these offenders to
OL,15,Ftask."JIn sentencing the three men,
OL,16,Fthe Judge also mentioned that the use
OL,17,Fof false registration plates in the
OL,18,Fcommission of the offence was an
OL,19,Faggravating factor. Costs were held
OL,20,Fover until a proceeds of crime hearing
OL,21,Frequested by the Environment Agency
OL,22,Fcould be heard.
