OL,6,FAn Environment Agency spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are glad to see the outcome
OL,8,Fof this prosecution.
OL,10,F"We gave extensive advice and guidance
OL,11,Fbut despite this, both Paul and
OL,12,FBenjamin Harrison failed to register
OL,13,Ffor the relevant permits and accepted
OL,14,Ffurther waste onto site.
OL,16,F"Illegal waste sites like this
OL,17,Fundermine legitimate businesses,
OL,18,Fundercut their prices, and blight the
OL,19,Fenvironment."
